des:
Listen in as Michele Bellisari a midlife mama, wife, Realtor, dog lover and consummate implementer of social media for branding and business shares daily tips, techniques, frustrations and successes as a real estate agent and entrepreneur. 

Speaker, blogger and video marketer she is also the founder of #SoooBoca Lifestyle Blog & Media that is based in Boca Raton, Florida focusing on local happenings, travel, beauty, biz, food and events in Boca, South Florida and Beyond! Sometime with her millennial daughters and sometimes solo! 

So join her for a daily sip, social, sell sesh that is short, sweet and occasionally sassy! 

PS...If you like interviews check out The Real Estate Influencer Buzz Podcast where Michele interviews influencers in and out of the real estate industry! You can find on Itunes, Buzzsprout, Stitcher, Google, Anchor and Spotify! 

Subscribe and Follow:
